  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients with diagnosis of Multiple Sclerosis or Clinically Isolated Syndrome who have been
        or will be treated with Betaferon.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with diagnosis of MS or CIS and decision taken by the physician to prescribe
             Betaferon

          -  Patients who have not participated in Betaferon regulatory Post Marketing Surveillance
             before.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Exclusion criteria must be read in conjunction with local product information
      </textblock>
